        "executive_summary": "Monterey Office delivered a Performance Score of 56 out of 100 (where 50 represents the network average), positioning the clinic slightly above the midline. The clinic matched the company average on Scheduler Compliance (81.1% vs. 81.14%) and Avg Delay (13.5 mins vs. 13.5 mins), while Chair Utilization of 87.0% aligned closely with the company benchmark of 86.96%. The primary operational friction point is Treatments Past Closing, which averaged 2.5 daily in February\u2014an area worth addressing to protect team wellbeing and operational predictability.",
