          "Monterey achieved 100.0% iAssign Utilization in February, reflecting complete adherence to the assignment system and demonstrating the clinic's discipline in adopting our scheduling tools. Nurse Utilization of 80.3% sits at a healthy operating level, neither stretched nor underutilized, allowing the care team to maintain quality while managing patient flow efficiently."
